			</div>
			<img src="img/environment/growing-algae.gif" alt="Growing Algae" />
		</div>
		<div class="stat4">
			<h4>Why tackle it now, though?</h4>
			<div class="img-wrapper">
				<img src="img/stopwatch.gif" alt="Stopwatch" />
				<img src="img/stopwatch.gif" alt="Stopwatch" />
				<img src="img/stopwatch.gif" alt="Stopwatch" />
			</div>
			<div>
				<span>Methane</span> has a shorter atmospheric life of 7-12 years compared
